# Build artefacts — _build/ holds compiled code, docs, and reports
**/_build
**/deps
**/.fetch

# Per-app coverage dirs (written by excoveralls; collected into _build/cover/ by mix test.coverage)
**/cover/**

# Erlang crash dumps
**/erl_crash.dump
**/*.ez

# BEAM bytecode (committed only if checked into release packages)
**/*.beam

# Runtime secrets — never commit these
**/config/*.secret.exs

# Escript binaries (built with `mix escript.build` in apps/cli)
**/apps/cli/cli

# Editor / tooling
**/.elixir_ls/
.elixir-tools/
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS artefacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

claude.session.sh

**/calculator_app_local.db
**/calculator_app_local.db*
